 Expanding access to comprehensive, compassionate healthcare for populations across the State of Illinois.  Making our university a welcoming community destination for meaningful, engaging experiences.  Empowering students with opportunities to be engaged citizens and work in partnership with communities.        Read about how we connect to communities            From the Theatre to the Hospital    Posted on April 03, 2020             Connecting with Indigenous Communities    Posted on November 26, 2019             Chancellor Amiridis Celebrates Donors and Advocates for Supporting UIC    Posted on April 11, 2019             UIC CHAMPIONS NETWork    Posted on March 01, 2019             UIC launches fundraising campaign to raise $750 million    Sherri McGinnis Gonzalez  |  Posted on October 30, 2017               Turning Brownfields into "Greenfields"    Janice Cantieri  |  Posted on June 27, 2017             Global grocer Boyede Sobitan    Kate Silver  |  Posted on April 20, 2017             The 606’s Trailblazer Jamie Simone    Jonathan Black  |  Posted on April 20, 2017             Inclusive Medicine: Robert Winn, MD    Posted on February 28, 2017             Impactful Medicine: Illinois Heart Rescue    Posted on February 28, 2017                 Make Your Impact  Choose a fund from our secure giving form to support connections to communities.   Give Now            IGNITE:  The Campaign for UIC    Back to main content           Give Now    IGNITE Priorities     Support Student Success    Empower Faculty    Drive Discoveries    Connect to Communities    Support A College or Unit      Understanding Giving     Giving Strategies    Gift Planning    How to Give                    UIC Logo        Advancement       Contact   601 S. Morgan Street, 2503 University Hall (MC 002), Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: 312-413-8272  advance@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  